name: Steel Rose by Stephen Adams
description:
Hand crafted steel roses by Stephen Adams. The stems are made from real barb wire so we recommend handling with care as the cuts, welds, and barbed wire can indeed poke someone. 

Since these are custom made they do vary piece by piece. Each one can range in size from approximately 9" to up to 12". This listing is for one steel rose. If you would like to custom order more, please contact us directly and we can work with you on the order.
